hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Another year regardiapharma.com SIR – An MP is rude to police officers doing their duty. He apologises. End of story, or so it should be. Any differences between the words he actually used, the words he later thought he had used, the words the officers thought he had used, and the words they later said he had used are completely irrelevant. A disgraceful amount of valuable police time has been wasted on investigating this irrelevance.
